parse

public QAReport parse(String dtd_version,
                      String file)
               throws XMLParseException,
                      ExternalResourceException
Parses the specified file into a QAReport. If the document is valid with respect to QAReport.dtd, the method constructs an QAReport object which reflects the information of the document.

Parameters:
dtd_version - the DTD Version
file - the file to parse
Returns:
the QAReport contained in the file
Throws:
ExternalResourceException - if failed to handle the event
XMLParseException - if failed to handle the event
